<div class="w-full lg:w-[40%] xl:w-[60%] mt-12 lg:mt-0">
  <p class="text-center">
    Füllen Sie das Kontaktformular aus und wir werden uns umgehend bei Ihnen
    melden.
  </p>
  <div class="rounded-md h-full flex flex-col space-y-4 mt-4">
    <div class="flex space-x-2">
      <input
        type="text"
        placeholder="Name"
        class="w-full border border-gray-300 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 placeholder:tracking-widest"
      />
      <input
        type="email"
        placeholder="Email"
        class="w-full border border-gray-300 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 placeholder:tracking-widest"
      />
    </div>
    <textarea
      rows={8}
      placeholder="Nachricht"
      class="w-full border border-gray-300 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 placeholder:tracking-widest"
    ></textarea>

    <div class="flex items-center text-xs space-x-2">
      <input type="checkbox" name="privacy-checkbox" id="privacy-checkbox"/><label for="privacy-checkbox"
        >Ich habe die Datenschutzerklärung gelesen und akzeptiere diese.
      </label>
    </div>

    <button
      class="px-4 mr-auto bg-brand-500 text-white rounded-md py-3 font-medium tracking-wide hover:bg-brand-700 transition-colors duration-100 ease-out hover relative"
    >
      Anfrage abschicken
    </button>
  </div>
</div>
